reviewText: Good information, well presented and fun to watch

WELL SINCE I HAVE ALWAYS BEEN A OLD WEST BUFF, THIS WAS RIGHT UP MY ALLEY. I HAVE BEEN TO HIS HOUSE AND GRAVE.
Get the real scoop on the real jesse james. this goes beyond the hollywood glamour portrayal that typically depicts jesse as a folk hero.

The DVD concerning Jesse James is interesting and informative.  For someone who never knew the real story surrounding Jesse James, it's very good.  I enjoyed watching the DVD very much and am glad to have it in my collection.
not disappointed. watched it several times. lots of info about jesse, some not seen before. yes, i'd recommend it.
